data.description: OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH A NICE WOOD BURNING STOVE IN LIVING ROOM. LARGE KITCHEN WITH PLENTY OF CUPBARDS AND A SKYLIGHT FOR ADDED NATURAL LIGHT.  BOTH BATHROOMS HAVE BEEN UPDATED WITH BEAUTIFUL TILE WORK.  ALL 4 BEDROOMS ARE NICE SIZES.  FAMILY ROOM DOWNSTAIRS HAS NEW CARPET AND PROVIDES A GREAT ADDITIONAL ENTERTAINMENT SPACE.  THE LAUNDRY ROOM HAS PLENTY OF ROOM FOR STORAGE OR EVEN ENOUGH ROOM FOR AN IN HOME OFFICE. ADDITIONAL ROOM ON HOME IS A BEAUTIFUL SUN ROOM WITH LOTS OF WINDOWS FOR THOSE PEACEFUL MORNING CUPS OF COFFEE.  HOME IS LOCATED ON A CULD-A-SAC WHICH PROVIDES FOR A VERY LARGE BACKYARD, ALLOWING LOTS OF ROOM FOR ANIMALS OR PLAY EQUIPMENT.  LARGE DRIVEWAY WHICH IS LARGE ENOUGH FOR MANY VEHICLES OR  RV.  COME AND SEE THE OPPORTUNITYS FOR THIS HOME.  SUNROOM MAY NOT BE INCLUDED IN ASSESSORS TOTAL SQ. FOOTAGE BUYER TO VERIFY SQ. FT.
